ementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Custom themes can use subclass of ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBulletListComponentTokensProvider","isActive":true},{"text":" and apply the provider they need.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"BulletListComponentTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"bullet list","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Bullet list","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" components tokens are defined with raw and semantic tokens of spaces (from ","type":"text"},{"code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":").","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemebulletlistcomponenttokensprovider"}}}